    "description_long": "This is a modern fire department SUV-style emergency response vehicle, primarily painted in white with a red hood and red accent stripes along the sides. The vehicle features black trim, a roof-mounted emergency light bar, and a small antenna or sensor on the roof. The side doors display the text 'SCFD' and additional fire department insignia, indicating its official use. The rear of the vehicle has visible taillights, a license plate, and additional emergency markings. The wheels are black with silver hubcaps, and the windows are tinted, suggesting a standard interior for personnel and equipment transport.",
